vocabInfos.mediumDef:
1) to be fulfilled, be completed, come to an end
1a) (P'al) to be fulfilled, be completed
1b) (Aphel) to put an end to
vocabInfos._es_Definition: (a) qal   llegar al final; (b) hif.   terminar, finalizar
